Narendra Modi in Delhi; BJP to declare him its choice for PM

Share EMAIL PRINT Workers wearing Modi masks celebrate outside the BJP headquarters in New Delhi.

New Delhi: has landed at Delhi airport and is headed into town in his SUV. This evening, he is expected to be named the BJP's candidate for prime minister in 2014.
